  <p><a id="TSJN-01-03-0730-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to They sailed  on the 12th. inst. in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0730-ks-0001">They sailed  on the 12th. inst.</a>: This obviously is an error by TJ; see <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0716" class="document">TJ to DAnmours, 9 Sep</a>., in which it is stated that the boats sail this day up the bay.</p></div>
